
'''Anita Ukah''' (yavutse 14 Kanama 1995) ni umukinnyi wa firime akaba n'umunyamideli muri  Nigeria  rwiyemezamirimo na Miss titleholder wari ikamba nk'uko wegukanye muri 2018 nk'Umukobwa mwiza cyane muri Nijeriya . Yambitse ikamba ry'umusimbura wa MBGN Umwamikazi Nyekachi Douglas muri 2019. Yaserukiye Nigeriya mu marushanwa ya Miss World 2018 yabaye ku ya 8 Ukuboza 2018 kuri Sanya City Arena i Sanya mu [[Ubushinwa|Bushinwa]], aho yaje muri Top 30 mu marushanwa ya Miss World . <ref>https://www.pulse.ng/lifestyle/events/mbgn-2018-anita-ukah-emerges-new-queen/erssf3r.amp</ref>

== Ubuzima bwo hambere ==
Ukah akomoka muri leta ya Imo kandi akomoka mu muryango w'abantu barindwi. <ref>https://www.sunnewsonline.com/i-dreamt-of-becoming-a-queen-at-tender-age-anita-ukah-mbgn-2018/</ref>

== Uburezi ==
Ukah ni umuhanga muri laboratoire yubuvuzi wize muri kaminuza ya Igbenedion, Okada arangiza muri 2016.

Amarushanwa ya mbere ya Anita yari muri kaminuza ye aho yatsindiye irushanwa rya Miss Igbinedion University Okada (IUO) mu 2014. <ref>https://dailytrust.com/how-i-became-the-most-beautiful-girl-in-nigeria-anita</ref> Muri 2018, Ukah yaserukiye leta ya Imo kumukobwa mwiza muri Nigeriya 2018. Kuri finale ikomeye yabereye muri Okara Cultural Centre i Yenagoa, Bayelsa, Yambitswe ikamba ryumukobwa mwiza muri Nijeriya . <ref>https://m.guardian.ng/life/nigerians-react-to-the-2018-most-beautiful-girl-in-nigeria-mbgn-pageant/</ref> <ref>https://www.premiumtimesng.com/entertainment/naija-fashion/285219-miss-imo-emerges-most-beautiful-girl-in-nigeria.html</ref>

